---
layout: main
title: Amount Sembark
sitemap:
  changefreq: monthy
  priority: 0.90
---

<main>
  <section class="container px-4 mx-auto py-24">
    <h1 class="text-5xl max-w-2xl font-medium text-indigo-50">
      Our mission is to empower travel businesses with tools that help them
      grow.
    </h1>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-indigo-800 py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="lg:flex lg:space-x-12">
        <section class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-3xl mb-8 text-indigo-100 font-medium">Our Story</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl text-indigo-200">
            We created Sembark for businesses that share our passion for using
            technology to empower travel businesses for better customer
            experience and growth. For many of us, great customer service isn't
            a cost center â€” it's an effective marketing tool, a competitive
            differentiator, and a cornerstone of the brand. Sembark was built
            with
            <b>"work together for better"</b> theme in mind and connects your
            sales, reservations and accounting for ease of management.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl text-indigo-200">
            But till 2018, there were no travel business management platforms
            available that embodied our technology-centric values. There were
            software that quite literally required to manage the software
            instead of software managing there business. These made it far too
            difficult for a long term growth. We felt a strong pull to make
            something different, and we did.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl text-indigo-200">
            Today Sembark is used by technology-centric organizations across
            India, from small businesses to high-growth startups and
            organizations. We've been on this journey for 1 year now and are
            still in early days. And we are hoping for really long run.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section class="lg:w-1/3 lg:mt-20">
          <ul
            class="
              grid
              sm:grid-cols-2
              lg:grid-cols-1
              rounded-lg
              bg-indigo-700
              text-center
              divide-y
              sm:divide-y-0 sm:divide-x
              lg:divide-y lg:divide-x-0
              divide-indigo-900
              hover:divide-transparent
            "
          >
            <li
              class="
                p-8
                hover:transform
                hover:scale-105
                hover:rounded-lg
                hover:shadow-lg
                hover:bg-indigo-700
                flex flex-col
                space-y-2
                duration-300
                ease
              "
            >
              <span>Launched in November of </span>
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold">2019</span>
              <span>remove from day one</span>
            </li>
            <li
              class="
                p-8
                hover:transform
                hover:scale-105
                hover:rounded-lg
                hover:shadow-lg
                hover:bg-indigo-700
                flex flex-col
                space-y-2
                duration-300
                ease
              "
            >
              <span>We serve customers in</span>
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold">10+</span>
              <span>cities in India</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-indigo-50 py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-8 text-indigo-900 font-medium text-center">
        Our Values
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-indigo-800 text-center">
        People love to buy from and support businesses they believe in. It's
        what makes small businesses so special, and it's why we choose to share
        our values publicly.
      </p>
      <section class="mt-16 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h4 class="text-2xl mb-8 text-indigo-900 font-medium">
          Do less, do it better
        </h4>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl text-indigo-800">
          Instead of chasing feature parity, we aspire to build products that
          get the details right. We're fiercely committed to helping our
          customers feel like they've got superpowers.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="px-4 py-24 bg-purple-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-12 text-purple-100 font-medium text-center">
        Meet Our Team
      </h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {% for member in team.members %}
        <div
          class="
            hover:shadow-xl
            p-8
            rounded-lg
            transition-colors
            duration-300
            hover:bg-purple-700
          "
        >
          <div class="text-center">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/{{ member.profile_img }}@2x.jpg"
              srcset="
                      /assets/images/{{ member.profile_img }}.jpg,
                      /assets/images/{{ member.profile_img }}@2x.jpg 2x,
                      /assets/images/{{ member.profile_img }}@3x.jpg 3x
              "
              alt="{{ member.name }}"
              class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full mb-8 block mx-auto"
            />
            <h5 class="text-lg font-medium">{{ member.name }}</h5>
            <p class="text-purple-200 my-2">
              <span>{{ member.designation }}</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-purple-300 text-sm">
              <span>{{ member.past }}</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
